defaultIn September 2013, 
defaultin addition to the above forums
default, the main operators established a Joint Operators Review (JOR) Working Group to further share best practice, to identify any changes that we can make, and to drive improvements in a coordinated way. 
default&#xa0;
default5.4
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThis Group was
default set up by, involves, and reports to 
defaultthe CEOs of the three 
defaultmain operators of helicopter services in the North Sea
default. 
defaultT
defaulthe JOR 
defaultis 
defaultto become the principal vehicle for safety improvement cooperation. Its mission is “to review current processes, procedures and equipment in order to identify best practice in the offshore helicopter industry with a view to further enhancing safety”. 
